
//1.直接更换的方式，只换背景

sudo cp ${picture-path} /usr/share/backgrounds/

sudo gedit /usr/share/gnome-shell/theme/ubuntu.css 

[change the following segment] 

#lockDialogGroup {

    background: #2c001e url(resource:///org/gnome/shell/theme/noise-texture.png);

    background-repeat: repeat; }

==>

#lockDialogGroup {

    background: #2c001e url(file:///usr/share/backgrounds/壁纸名称);

    background-repeat: no-repeat;

    background-size: cover;

    background-position: center; }




//2.更换图片和主题，安装
解压Ubunterra.tar.xz 直接./install.sh
原来配置的 /usr/share/gnome-shell/theme/ubuntu.css 会备份到 ./Ubunterra/bin下
